    {
      "bookmarkId": "26295687_9_10113-10229",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "10113-10229",
      "markText": "事实上，这样一台自动印刷机必将印出自人类学会写字以来所有人写过的所有东西：每一行散文和诗歌、每张报纸上的每一篇社论和广告、每一部沉闷的科学论著、每一封情书、每一张留给送奶工的纸条……",
      "totalCount": 736,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26295687&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10113&rangeEnd=10229",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d8732de071913d87d8751c1?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10113&rangeEnd=10229"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26295687_9_13328-13368",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "13328-13368",
      "markText": "事实上，在无穷数的世界里，部分可能等于整体！",
      "totalCount": 580,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26295687&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=13328&rangeEnd=13368",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d8732de071913d87d8751c1?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=13328&rangeEnd=13368"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26295687_9_19007-19069",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "19007-19069",
      "markText": "ℵ₀代表所有整数的数量，ℵ₁代表所有几何点的数量，ℵ₂代表曲线的所有种类，但截至目前，还没有任何人能找到可以记作ℵ₃的集合。",
      "totalCount": 516,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26295687&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=19007&rangeEnd=19069",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d8732de071913d87d8751c1?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=19007&rangeEnd=19069"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26295687_12_15017-15067",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "15017-15067",
      "markText": "比如说，糖就有左旋和右旋两种，不管你信不信，以糖为食的细菌也分为两种，每种细菌都只能吃对应手性的糖。",
      "totalCount": 476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26295687&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=15017&rangeEnd=15067",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d8732de071913d87d8751c1?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=15017&rangeEnd=15067"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26295687_9_5013-5039",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "5013-5039",
      "markText": "事实上，宇宙中每立方米的空间内平均只有大约1个原子。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26295687&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5013&rangeEnd=5039",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d8732de071913d87d8751c1?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5013&rangeEnd=5039"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26295687_14_4319-4389",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "4319-4389",
      "markText": "四维几何学认为空间和时间只是恒定不变的四维距离在对应轴上的投影，因此我们必然得出上述结论。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26295687&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=4319&rangeEnd=4389",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d8732de071913d87d8751c1?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=4319&rangeEnd=4389"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26295687_9_10400-10457",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "10400-10457",
      "markText": "要是出版商的地下室里有这么一台机器，那他们只需要从大量垃圾里挑出这些佳作进行编辑就好——反正他们现在也是这么干的。",
      "totalCount": 464,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26295687&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10400&rangeEnd=10457",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d8732de071913d87d8751c1?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10400&rangeEnd=10457"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26295687_9_11274-11308",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "11274-11308",
      "markText": "是的，想从这些自动印刷的材料里面挑出任何东西，你都得花很多很多时间！",
      "totalCount": 459,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26295687&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11274&rangeEnd=11308",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d8732de071913d87d8751c1?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11274&rangeEnd=11308"
    },
    {
